{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/about/exhibition/the-power-in-your-hands","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The splayed hand, the clenched fist; political movements often deploy the symbolic power of the hand. Its image evokes protest and the refusal to submit, conveys agency and the desire for self-determination. Bound or shackled hands signal enslavement and de-humanisation. The extended hand supports those in need, reaches out across divisions, and seals the bond between individuals, communities, and nations.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"December 11, 2020","slug":"/about/exhibition/the-power-in-your-hands","title":"The Power in your Hands","order":7,"featuredImgUrl":"https://content.fitz.ms/fitz-website/assets/rodinhand.jpg?key=directus-large-crop&q=50","featuredImgAlt":"Rodin Hand"},"featuredImg":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":400,"height":300,"srcSet":"/static/9978c3c417902349e00b5ca5ed28f5b7/2244e/rodinhand.jpg 1x,\n/static/9978c3c417902349e00b5ca5ed28f5b7/4fe8c/rodinhand.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/9978c3c417902349e00b5ca5ed28f5b7/14b42/rodinhand.jpg 2x","src":"/static/9978c3c417902349e00b5ca5ed28f5b7/2244e/rodinhand.jpg"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/about/exhibition/the-power-in-your-hands"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3576823491","3649515864","63159454"]}